Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,書也念了 考試也過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我到公司了 先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一會聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 新人研修準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來今年的新人研修\N好像改變時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她在同期裡算是很積極的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓他破例晉升呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,銷售還是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,還是要快點去現場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,, -我說啊 -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,銷售部的儀容很重要 你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才看了一下嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的絲襪破了 -欽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,（愛好絲襪的中年男人們）\N（多次侵犯絕品辦公室女郎）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟上司和部下沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,趁著還是溫熱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我出去比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,, -給我看看吧 -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,, -就這樣吧 -我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的作戰計劃要記住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,商場上的客套話\N新員工要都學會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,, -知道嗎 -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這個茶很好 可以排毒 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,, -這個茶有利尿作用吧\N -就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,, -很好喝 -是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,, -還要嗎 -我之後再喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,, -我知道了 -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好好喝完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,（故障中）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,歎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽到警報聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是女廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你有探測器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告訴上司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你去說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果拍了你的裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,, -什麼意思\N -如果還有在別的地方拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就會上傳到網路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,, -給我看看 -你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你舔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以尿出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是很髒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的尿液
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了 你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有屁股 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你吸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
