Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
