Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
