Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了 你的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,, -好完美啊 -什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的好完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,歎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個跟你的是 一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,, 一樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
