Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,皮膚好白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是不是涼颼颼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有什麼變化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,, -這裡哦 -不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我聞味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要摸這裡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好美的屁股啊
